@startuml
skinparam stateBackgroundColor LightBlue
skinparam stateBorderColor DarkBlue
skinparam stateArrowColor DarkSlateGray
skinparam stateFontSize 12
skinparam noteBackgroundColor LightYellow

title MyAIStorybook FYP-2 — State Diagram: Story Lifecycle

[*] --> IDLE : System ready

IDLE --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : User submits prompt\n(text or voice)

PROMPT_RECEIVED --> STT_PROCESSING : [voice input selected]
STT_PROCESSING --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : Whisper transcribes audio\n[text returned to input field]

PROMPT_RECEIVED --> VALIDATING : Prompt submitted to backend

VALIDATING --> IDLE : [Invalid / Nonsense] → Error returned
VALIDATING --> GENERATING_TEXT : [Valid prompt]

GENERATING_TEXT --> REVIEWING : Writer Agent completes\nstory draft

REVIEWING --> GENERATING_TEXT : [Coherence check failed]\nRetry (max 2x)
REVIEWING --> EDITING : [Story approved by\nReviewer Agent]

EDITING --> EXPORTING_PDF : Editor finalizes\n& triggers PDF export

EXPORTING_PDF --> IMAGE_GENERATION : [generate_images = true]\nOllama paused (GPU freed)

state IMAGE_GENERATION {
    [*] --> GENERATING_SCENE_1
    GENERATING_SCENE_1 --> GENERATING_SCENE_2 : txt2img → img2img done
    GENERATING_SCENE_2 --> GENERATING_SCENE_3 : txt2img → img2img done
    GENERATING_SCENE_3 --> [*] : All scenes done
    note right of GENERATING_SCENE_1
        Personalized: IP-Adapter FaceID
        Simple: Standard Stable Diffusion
    end note
}

IMAGE_GENERATION --> COMPLETED : Images saved\nOllama resumed

EXPORTING_PDF --> COMPLETED : [generate_images = false]\nText-only story returned

COMPLETED --> EVALUATING : Evaluation Agent\nstarted (background)
note right of EVALUATING
    Async subprocess:
    - CLIP image-text alignment
    - CLIP visual consistency
    - Sentence Transformer coherence
    - Flesch-Kincaid readability
    - Story structure heuristic
    - InsightFace (personalized only)
    Saves JSON to generated/evaluations/
end note

EVALUATING --> COMPLETED : Evaluation done\n(score saved)

COMPLETED --> NARRATING : User clicks Play
NARRATING --> NARRATING : User changes page /\nswitches voice
NARRATING --> COMPLETED : User stops playback

COMPLETED --> CHATTING : User opens Character Chat
CHATTING --> CHATTING : Multi-turn conversation
CHATTING --> COMPLETED : User closes chat

COMPLETED --> WORKSHOP : User starts Idea Workshop
WORKSHOP --> WORKSHOP : Multi-turn requirements\ncollection
WORKSHOP --> PROMPT_RECEIVED : Requirements complete\n→ Auto-generate story

COMPLETED --> [*] : Session ends

' Error transitions
GENERATING_TEXT --> ERROR : [LLM unavailable /\nMax retries exceeded]
IMAGE_GENERATION --> COMPLETED : [Image generation fails]\nGraceful degradation\n(text-only story)
STT_PROCESSING --> ERROR : [Whisper model error]
ERROR --> IDLE : User retries

@enduml
